We believe elevating where you live is about merging it seamlessly with how you live. We have gone great distances to design amenities and choose locations that put everything within reach. Where you live, is where you come alive.<br>
<br>
In an area flourishing with convenience, recreation, culture and possibility, with a delicious array of cuisines at popular restaurants including Rich Table, Gary Danko, and Doppio Zero. Here, you’ll also find easy access to a host of services from hospitals and hotels to schools and travel agencies in the vicinity.<br>
Avalon Hayes Valley offers San Francisco apartments in Lower Haight. Inside our refreshing smoke-free community, you'll find thoughtfully-designed studio, one- and two-bedroom apartments and townhomes. Imagine entertaining in a gourmet kitchen and enjoying city views from large bay windows. Our technology package, AvalonConnect, offers pre-installed high-speed and community-wide WiFi, powered by Xfinity by Comcast, providing instant internet access for residents and guests. Live your life effortlessly with amenities that include a fitness center and beautifully landscaped rooftop terraces with outdoor seating and barbecues. Not to mention you will be living in the heart of San Francisco near downtown, Civic Center, the Mission, SOMA and the Castro.<br>
<br>
This is not just apartment living. This is living up.<br>
